    "attributes": {
        "action": "Divert 15% of BBC licence fee income instead of the budget's taxes on farms",
        "additional_details": "I believe there would be no material impact on viewers and that this would help ensure no loss of farms or food security issues. I think this is a better way of raising the money.",
        "background": "The BBC\u2019s licence fee income in 2023-24 was \u00a33.7bn. Agricultural property relief and business property relief changes in the budget are forecast to raise \u00a30.52bn/year by the end of the forecast in 2029-30. Government should instead divert 15% of the licence fee income to raise \u00a30.55bn/year.",
